data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged.  If You’re Looking for an Estate Home on an OVER-SIZED HOMESITE in a Gated Community that Checks ALL the BOXES, Your Search Has Ended. . . This Home Offers a Custom Pool & Spa Built by Aqua Tech (2019) with a Private and Peaceful Preserve and a Peek-A-Boo Lake View for the Ultimate in Privacy, 4 Bedrooms, 2.5 Baths, plus a FULL-SIZED 3-Car Garage on a Private Cul-De-Sac Street with 2668 sq. ft. of One-Floor Living (No Stairs,) this Could Be the Home You’ve Been Waiting For. Affordably Priced for the Couple or Family that Needs Extra Space, this Home is the LOWEST PRICED PER SQUARE FOOTAGE ONE-STORY POOL/SPA HOME in Gran Paradiso! Detailed Archways and Columns, Elegant Leaded Glass Front Entry Door, 10-Foot Ceilings and 8-Foot Doorways, Crown Molding in ALL Public Rooms + the Master Bedroom Suite, Tile Set on the Diagonal (Public Rooms) and Each Bedroom has Luxury Vinyl Flooring (No Carpet.) The Gourmet Kitchen Features a Neary New GE PROFILE CONVECTION DOUBLE WALL OVEN with an Air-Fryer (2022), GE Profile Microwave (2021), Glass Cooktop (2016), Glazed Honey-Maple Cabinetry and Granite Counters. Step Outside onto the Covered Lanai and Gaze Upon Your Luxurious SALTWATER Pool & Spa with a CLEARVIEW SCREEN Surrounded by Luxurious Landscaping. You Have Arrived at Your Own PERSONAL PARADISE!  The Spacious Master Suite Leads to the En-Suite Bath with Dual Vanities, Luxury Soaking Tub, and Seamless Glass Shower.  An OVER-SIZED WALK-IN MASTER CLOSET completes the Master Suite. The 3-Car Garage has an Epoxy Coated Floor, Over-Head Storage Racks with  a Pre-Wired Generac Homelink 30 amp Manual Transfer Switch with Wall-Mounted Receptacle/Hookup for a Portable Generator and an EXTRA ELECTRICAL PANEL for a Future GENERATOR HOOK-UP CONNECTION. Most Recent UPDATES; NEW Hot Water Heater and NEW Garage Door Opener (8/28/23.) The Spectacular Gran Paradiso Tuscan-style Clubhouse with its State-of-the-Art Fitness Center, Resort-style Heated Saltwater Community Pool with Beach Entry, Hot-Tub, Cabanas, and Brick-Paver Decking is the Social Place to Be to Meet Up with New Friends. A Full-time Lifestyle Director will Keep You Busy Playing Pickleball and Tennis, along with Plenty of Social Events, Billiards, Card Games and Other Fun Activities. Schedule a Massage, Followed by a Trip to the Steam Room and Finish with a Sauna ALL ON SITE in the Fitness Center. Right Outside Gran Paradiso is the NEW Community of Wellen Park, One of the Fastest Growing Master-planned Communities in the United States with Shops, Restaurants, and an 80-Acre Lake for Recreational Boating, Community Events and so Much More. You’re 15 Minutes Away from the Amazing Gulf of Mexico Beaches, Boating on the Intercoastal Waterway and Several Golf Courses. The Atlanta Braves Spring Training Stadium is Just 5 Minutes from Your Doorstep. Drive 15 to 20 Minutes to Charming Venice Island for Outdoor Cafes and Quaint Shops. Schedule Your Private Showing Today and Come See Your Future Home.
